text: Just one person and he's currently out on his wedding. I believe he has someone covering for him tho. But still a bit slower right now.

First off - let me thank you for contributing to the Marketplace!! Super cool, excited to see what you've put together.

Secondly, we have a small (1-person) team that manually checks and bug tests all submissions. So it takes awhile. They are shooting for 24 hour turn around time, however, with a flood of new submissions + INBOUND Conference + he's on his wedding and has someone new covering ... it may take a little bit.

Thanks for your patience, it will smooth out over time and get much faster.

If you don't hear back in a week, please DM me and I'll dig into it a bit more.
